erto.\r\n\r\nVenha tomar um caf√© com a gente! Escreva para <a title=\"comunidade@olabi.co\" href=\"mailto:comunidade@olabi.co\">comunidade@olabi.co</a> e agende a sua visita. Ser√° um prazer conhece-lo e pensar como trabalhamos em conjunto![/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class=\"fb-like-box\" data-href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Olabi/1488824461358960\" data-width=\"460\" data-height=\"250\" data-colorscheme=\"light\" data-show-faces=\"true\" data-header=\"false\" data-stream=\"false\" data-show-border=\"false\"></div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Sobre','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-v1','','','2014-10-21 02:57:46','2014-10-21 02:57:46','',17,'http://olabi.me/2014/10/17-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1199,2,'2014-09-11 01:15:40','2014-09-11 01:15:40','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1409941789198{background-color: #7fa4b0 !important;}\" fullwidth=\"1\" ewf_row_title=\"Full width\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][ewf-team-member name=\"Sample Name\" job_title=\"Job Title\" url_facebook=\"http://www.facebook.com/silviosantos\" url_linkedin=\"http://br.linkedin.com/silvio-santos\" image_id=\"946\"]I am test text block. Click edit button to change this text.[/ewf-team-member][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][ewf-team-member name=\"Sample Name\" job_title=\"Job Title\" url_facebook=\"http://www.facebook.com/silviosantos\" url_linkedin=\"http://br.linkedin.com/silvio-santos\" image_id=\"946\"]I am test text block. Click edit button to change this text.[/ewf-team-member][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][ewf-team-member name=\"Sample Name\" job_title=\"Job Title\" url_facebook=\"http://www.facebook.co